title: JAM Trance Mini Wireless Speaker
description: Light up the room (or the tent or the patio) with the ultra-portable, super-lightweight JAM Trance Mini. In addition to big sound, this speaker packs fun flair — 36 different LED light programs cast a glow while you get down. Wireless technology means you can pair it with any Bluetooth device up to 30 feet away.
